turnkey-pde (1.1) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Initial release (1.0) TurnKey Portable Development Environment
    - LXC and LXD from Ubuntu xenial-backports
    - dnsmasq provides DNS for container domains .lxc and .lxd
    - lxc-turnkey template and inithooks.conf from TurnKey LXC appliance
    - lxd-turnkey downloads lxc v1 image and converts to lxd v2 image

     John Carver <dude4linux@gmail.com>  Tue, 06 Feb 2018 00:00:00 -0500

  * Release (1.1) 
    - bug fixes
    - updated version of lxc-turnkey template
    - apt-cacher-ng apt caching proxy for all containers
    - new lxd-make-image for tkldev appliance

